description: CW Bancorp operates as a holding company for CommerceWest Bank that provides various commercial banking services for small and mid-sized businesses in California. The company offers personal checking account, checking account, money market deposit account, savings account, sweep accounts, business accounts, attorney client trust accounts, and personal certificate of deposits It also provides loans, including lines of credit, commercial real estate loan, asset based, mergers and acquisitions, international, and term loan. In addition, the company offers remote deposit solutions; and online banking, mobile banking, and treasury management services. CW Bancorp was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Irvine, California.
